The '''D'farians''' were a member species of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] who allied themselves with the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] and the [[Diamal]]a during the [[Caamas Document]] crisis. D'farian vessels fought alongside the Diamala during a [[Battle of Bothawui (Galactic Civil War)|battle at Bothawui]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

